{"tid":1205750,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你哋嘅下一代 係會知道你哋做緊咩","createTime":"2019-06-11T23:20:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T23:20:23.000Z","uid":139645,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"43de03f81eac306801b0141f296c3b75150515a3","tid":1205750,"uid":139645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T23:20:23.000Z","msg":"真正既香港人 見到呢啲情況 見到自己屋企變成咁 自己人咁辛苦抗爭 一定覺得好無奈 好嬲 好傷心 <br />\n<br />\n當全香港市民上下一心反惡法 罷課罷市<br />\n然後一班警察阻止社會進步 阻止行動仲升級 你地推動香港淪陷既進程 <br />\n你的良心過意得去咩？定係你地毅進未學到咩係公義？咩係人權？<br />\n你地無資格做香港人 定你地根本唔係香港人係新移民？<br />\n低賤真係低賤<br />\n淨係會話自己保持中位 收order 做野 乜你地無靈魂？無批判思考？<br />\n就係知道自己除左警察之外 以咁既學歷 根本無可能搵到兩萬蚊 所以埋沒良心做警察 就以為可以高人一等 有特權 <br />\n而家時代唔同 今次我地聲音遍佈全球 你地既所作所為全世界都望住 <br />\n希望你地既下一代睇返國際新聞 發現自己爸爸媽媽係黑警 見到你地d相 幾咁躁狂 失去理智 打到手無寸鐵既市民留哂血 趴晒地 佢哋憎你哋一世 亦會因爲咁而感到羞恥<br />\n<br />\n你不配做香港人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUw7wmU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUw7wmU.png&h=6ad2ae00&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jb2KyAg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjb2KyAg.png&h=0c86a0e5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EEE80fh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEEE80fh.png&h=3376ac43&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VoY52tD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVoY52tD.png&h=4a18b88e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hoeXTAk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhoeXTAk.png&h=383f8850&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EN9pyAm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEN9pyAm.png&h=55abea5b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fcAswm2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfcAswm2.png&h=5d52adb6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WA7OfOJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thum